Other tools in metid

Xiaotao Shen (https://www.shenxt.info/)

Created on 2020-03-28 and updated on 2022-01-07

Source: vignettes/other_tools.Rmd
other_tools.Rmd

There are also a lot of useful tools in metid.

Read MS2 data

Read msp format file using readMGF 

result <- readMGF(file)

Read mzXML format file using readMZXML 

result <- readMZXML(file, threads = 3)

Read MGF format file using readMGF 

result <- readMGF(file)
